---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24">
    <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-purple-200/50 p-16">
      
      <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-600 leading-tight mb-6">
        Documentation Work
      </h1>

      <p class="text-base text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-12">
        A selection of documentation projects focused on clarity, real-world use cases, and scalable structure.
      </p>

      <hr class="border-gray-200 mb-12" />

      <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-600 mb-8">
        Featured Documentation
      </h2>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/50 to-blue-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-teal-100/50 mb-6">
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-4">
          Linux Firewall Configuration Guide
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-gray-600">
          <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Tools:</strong> Ubuntu, UFW, GitHub Pages</li>
          <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Focus:</strong> Beginner-friendly firewall setup</li>
          <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Status:</strong> <span class="text-green-600 font-medium">Complete</span></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a 
            href="/docs/linux-firewall" 
            class="bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium transition-colors shadow-md text-sm inline-block"
          >
            View Documentation
          </a>
          <a 
            href="https://github.com/Khanum49/linux-firewall-guide" 
            target="_blank"
            class="bg-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 text-teal-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium border-2 border-teal-600 transition-colors text-sm inline-block"
          >
            View Source on GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50/50 to-pink-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-purple-100/50 mb-12">
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-4">
          Inter-VLAN Routing Configuration
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-gray-600">
          <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Tools:</strong> Cisco Packet Tracer, Router-on-a-Stick</li>
          <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Focus:</strong> Network segmentation and inter-VLAN communication</li>
          <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Status:</strong> <span class="text-green-600 font-medium">Complete</span></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a 
            href="/docs/inter-vlan" 
            class="bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium transition-colors shadow-md text-sm inline-block"
          >
            View Documentation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-gray-200 mb-12" />

      <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-600 mb-8">
        Technical Articles
      </h2>

      <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/50 to-blue-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-teal-100/50">
          <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
            ESP32 Microcontroller: Features and Applications
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Overview of ESP32 capabilities, IoT applications, and real-world project examples</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">IoT</span>
            <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Embedded Systems</span>
          </div>
          <a 
            href="/docs/esp32" 
            class="bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors shadow-md text-sm inline-block"
          >
            Read Article
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50/50 to-pink-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-purple-100/50">
          <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
            STM32 and ARM Cortex-M: Architecture and Applications
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Understanding STM32 microcontrollers and ARM Cortex-M processor architecture</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">ARM</span>
            <span class="bg-pink-100 text-pink-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Microcontrollers</span>
          </div>
          <a 
            href="/docs/stm32" 
            class="bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors shadow-md text-sm inline-block"
          >
            Read Article
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/50 to-blue-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-teal-100/50">
          <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
            RTOS vs Bare Metal Firmware: Choosing the Right Approach
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Comparing Real-Time Operating Systems and Bare Metal programming for embedded systems</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">RTOS</span>
            <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Firmware</span>
          </div>
          <a 
            href="/docs/rtos-baremetal" 
            class="bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors shadow-md text-sm inline-block"
          >
            Read Article
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-gray-200 mb-12" />

      <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-600 mb-8">
        In Progress
      </h2>

      <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50/50 to-pink-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-purple-100/50">
          <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
            Sphinx Documentation Project
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Status:</strong> Building</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Includes custom CSS and a feedback button experiment</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/50 to-blue-50/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-teal-100/50">
          <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">
            Open Source Contribution Walkthrough
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Status:</strong> Writing</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Documenting the process of contributing to an open-source documentation project</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-gray-200 mb-12" />

      <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-600 mb-6">
        Open Source Contribution
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Merged contribution to an open-source documentation project (rstdoc). Successfully contributed documentation improvements and fixes to help improve the project's clarity and usability.
      </p>

      <a 
        href="https://github.com/rstdoc/rstdoc/pull/2" 
        target="_blank"
        class="bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium transition-colors shadow-md text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
        View on GitHub
      </a>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <a 
          href="/" 
          class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 font-medium inline-flex items-center"
        >
          ‚Üê Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>